{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1110805,"duration_api_ms":1061071,"num_turns":159,"result":"The fix is complete. Let me provide a summary of what was done:\n\n## Summary\n\nThe issue was that the DVC codebase was written for Python 3.6-3.11 and used internal pathlib API methods (`_from_parts`, `_init`, `_cparts`) that were removed/changed in Python 3.12. This caused the test infrastructure to completely fail.\n\n### Changes Made\n\n**`dvc/path_info.py`**:\n1. Fixed `PathInfo.__new__` to use Python 3.12-compatible `object.__new__(cls)` + `__init__(*args)` instead of removed `cls._from_parts(args)`\n2. Added `__new__` methods to `WindowsPathInfo` and `PosixPathInfo` to override the inherited behavior and prevent recursion\n3. Fixed the `isin` method to use `_parts_normcase_cached` instead of the removed `_cparts` attribute\n\n**`tests/dir_helpers.py`**:\n1. Fixed `TmpDir.__new__` with the same Python 3.12-compatible approach\n2. Added `__new__` methods to `WindowsTmpDir` and `PosixTmpDir` to properly handle their inheritance from `TmpDir`\n3. Added `scheme = \"local\"` to the concrete classes (since `PurePosixPath`/`PureWindowsPath` no longer define `scheme` in Python 3.12)\n\n### Results\n- All 5 expected failing tests (`test_collect_with_not_existing_dvcfile` × 4, `test_missing_deps` × 1) now **PASS**\n- All 24 `test_path_info.py` tests continue to **PASS**\n- All 10 `test_base.py` tests continue to **PASS**","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"31a5f657-6dd9-4c3d-99d7-ae35ffff215a","total_cost_usd":20.441123249999993,"usage":{"input_tokens":6112908,"cache_creation_input_tokens":833,"cache_read_input_tokens":556530,"output_tokens":46016,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"cache_deleted_input_tokens":0,"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed":{"inputTokens":6513315,"outputTokens":48179,"cacheReadInputTokens":584565,"cacheCreationInputTokens":833,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":20.441123249999993,"contextWindow":196000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"599f2b85-ac8a-4161-9eb3-0d950e9606de"}
